Tag, der - o dia, "the day"
Tasche, die - a bolsa, "the purse", "the bag"
Telefon, das - o telefone, "the telephone"
Terrace, die - o terraço
Theater, das - o teatro, "the theater"
Theatervorstellung - a peça (de teatro), "the play (theater)"
Tier, das - o animal, "the animal"
Tipp, der - a dica, "the tip"
Tisch, der - a mesa, "the table"
Tischtennis, das - o tênis de mesa (jogo, esporte), "the table tennis"
Tochter, die - a filha, "the daughter"
Toilette, die - o banheiro, "the toilete"
Tür, die - a porta, "the door"
